    <h1>Generating dunning letters</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Orders » Fulfillment » Generate dunning letters</strong></p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_generating_dunning_letters">1. Generating dunning letters</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In this menu, dunning letters are generated with the help of a <strong>group function</strong>. By selecting the corresponding search filter settings, you could e.g. generate dunning letters for <strong>all of the orders from a specific time period</strong> that are still currently in <strong>status [3] waiting for payment</strong>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_options">2. Options</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can carry out settings related to the layout of the dunning letters by going to <strong>Settings &gt; Orders &gt; Documents</strong>.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <strong>Settings &gt; Orders &gt; Event procedures</strong> in order to define which additional <strong>procedure(s)</strong> should be carried out when the dunning letter is generated.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_generating_dunning_letters_2">3. Generating dunning letters</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="admonitionblock note">
<table>
<tbody><tr>
<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-note" title="Note"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Generating dunning letters:</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <strong>Generate dunning letters</strong> (see path above).</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Pay attention to the explanations given in table 1 and carry out the <strong>settings</strong> for the <strong>search filter</strong> as desired.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Under <strong>procedure</strong>, select the order status that you would like to have assigned to the selected orders after the dunning letters were successfully created. Additionally, enter a <strong>comment</strong> if desired.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Click on the <strong>gear-wheel icon</strong> after having selected all of the options.<br>
→ You will receive a <strong>PDF file</strong>, which contains the dunning letters of all the orders that match the filter options you selected.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
