</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item ID</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">You have the possibility of creating a <strong>dunning charge</strong> as a separate item. Once you have done this, you can enter the corresponding <strong>item ID of the dunning charge</strong> here. This will then automatically be added to all of the dunning letters that are generated.</p></td>
</tr>
