<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Comment</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">You can compose a <strong>text</strong> here, which you would like to have appear on all of the dunning letters <strong>underneath the stock units</strong>.</p></td>
